OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStudy contradicts Rees-Mogg
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover hydrogen for heating  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A new study has cast doubt on          
OL,6, government claims that hydrogen could  
OL,7, be used to heat homes and so cut       
OL,8, greenhouse gas emissions.              
OL,10,FThe report, published in the journal   
OL,11,FJoule, analysed more than 30 studies   
OL,12,Fthat looked at hydrogen and heating.   
OL,14,FAll those studies found that hydrogen  
OL,15,Fwas much less efficient and more costly
OL,16,Fthan alternatives like heat pumps      
OL,18,FLast week the Business Secretary Jacob 
OL,19,FRees-Mogg told the Commons that        
OL,20,Fhydrogen was a "silver bullet".        
